public class BodyExtractorWalker
extends Walker

Walks a jimple AST and constructs the method bodies for all the methods of the SootClass associated with this walker (see constructor). note: Contrary to the plain "Walker", this walker does not create a SootClass, or interact with the scene. It merely adds method bodies for each of the methods of the SootClass it was initialized with.
